# This project does not ship Dockerfiles/compose files yet, but this
# .dockerignore is prepared for when you add containerization so secrets
# and build artifacts are never baked into images.

**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.vite

**/target
**/*.class
**/*.jar

**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.venv
**/venv

.git
.gitignore
.dockerignore
**/.idea
**/.vscode
*.md
!README.md
